#message:03:0F0
{
[Style Right]
Heyyyyy. [HEART][BR]
You're Lip, aren't you?[BR]
[Pause 10]I heard you used to be a fairy.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
I've always WANTED to smash[BR]
a fairy![BR]
[Pause 10]Boy, this is Goombarius's lucky day![BR]
[Wait][Next]
[Wave]I'll go easy, don't worry.[/fx][BR]
[Pause 10]Might even throw in some flowers[BR]
as a bonus, ya know?[BR]
[Wait][End]
}

