#message:03:0F3
{
[Style Right]
[CustomVoice soundIDs=0x207C,0x207D][Volume percent=72]
Young sir...[BR]
[Pause 10]I am a void spirit, for you have yet[BR]
to know my name.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
My plea says you and I will meet[BR]
eventually, but for now you should[BR]
know that your journey is yours and[BR]
yours alone.[BR]
[Wait][Next]
Select your path, good sir.[BR]
[Yield][End]
}

